Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:06.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我開門見山地問了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:17.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,請聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:21.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,拜託了  我們一起…烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,阻止她
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:38.83,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:38.83,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的這份躁動  是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.59,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.59,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像將臉埋入剛洗過的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:53.72,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:53.72,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥兒們吟唱著  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:04.78,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:04.78,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論走到哪  這道路都會延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:13.88,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:13.88,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牽手  更像是緊握這手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.65,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:20.65,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.01,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.01,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空為毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:31.25,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:31.25,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌對面的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:39.69,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:39.69,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}為你指向盡頭之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:49.20,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:49.20,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才該說謝謝你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:05.02,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1279.333,915.467)}生命之花仰望鳥兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,請詳細說明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:08.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,為了治療這病  我們去了各種各樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:13.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是日子一天天過去卻沒有任何線索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:15.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,就在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,在某個邊境之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們遇到了一個占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個占卜師看著我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,是血被玷汙之人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:33.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,若不淨化這血液  你便無永無安寧之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,汙穢之血會以新的血液得以淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊應該還記得那個占卜師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此將索瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,有了你的血  說不定海特拉就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:36.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,我都約好要永遠和爸爸在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:52.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.63,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,乖乖聽話  不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,同時他也是個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,我完全找不到治療的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類的病誰都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,也不能和別人說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是海特拉的身體卻越來越差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,我以為只要喝下健康人類的血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,說不定他的病就能好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:24.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,身體有沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒有  只是稍微濕了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,等下  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以不要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,擦下頭髮  不然會著涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,我只能依靠些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算傷害別人  就算背上罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算如此只要是為了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明你就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,明明想永遠和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我卻沒能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,我沒能做到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,還冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,不冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊真是愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個  真的對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,你做我朋友就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆先生  關於烏佐伊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  我已經沒有追責的打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,對於戀人來講這是理所當然的行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,我將其理解為家人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,我沒有作為烏佐伊家人的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你不覺得很像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,從身為人類的我皮膚上長出來的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,與烏佐伊的眼睛周圍和身體上長出來的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃了烏佐伊的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,曾經我和為數不多幾位人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,為了躲避異形  四處躲藏求生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,和我最重要的家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:06.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,有一天村子突然被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,是異形們的人類狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,同伴們  女兒的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,都接二連三被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,若是反抗手臂就會被撕毀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,想要逃跑就會被扭下雙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:55.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,其中還有被當場吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,總算逃到森林洞窟裡的我們還算幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  想到之後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,或許這不應稱為幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:38.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為害怕不知何時會到來的異形  精神飽受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,夜晚也不能好好入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒有像樣的食物和水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,就這樣過了兩天  三天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:51.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們三個都到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去看看外面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,異形…就在這麼近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們也得變得和他們一樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,不變成背離人道的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,就活不下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,吃了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,老…公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,好疼啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:37.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我沒有資格成為她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,至今為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直被欺騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,風變得更強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,說不定會變得狂暴起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們稍微繞一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:16.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,轉西邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊你的那份早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,我沒食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,昨天夜晚裡發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:39.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,真不知道該說你是遲鈍還是機敏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗你有被欺騙過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,欺騙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  就是欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是一個讓一直以來的美好的回憶都變成虛妄的殘酷謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我真是太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直被欺騙著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為謊言成為的父女  無法成為真正的父女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為烏佐伊和索瑪麗都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,突然發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,是龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:27.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,所有人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:36.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉你也會被捲走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,現在去也只會引起二次災害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,我已經確認了被捲走的方向和風的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,從地形上來看  兩人平安無事的概率很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,風停後馬上去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,嘴裡都是沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:35.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:43.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,你剛才說因為謊言成為的家人不是真正的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,但這份喜歡的情感卻不是假的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗喜歡爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊喜歡海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,參照索瑪麗他們的體重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,和風的強度和方向的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,她們兩個人應該在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:19.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊或許是聽到了昨天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直欺騙著烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,再也無法像以前一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  審判的時刻來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,審判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,對自己曾經犯下的罪行進行審判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,無論結果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,必須直面所需要贖罪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使那樣會背負更深罪業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:01.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,是影足鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:20.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,地盤意識很強烈  性情極具攻擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是冒然接近不僅我們會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,也會連累索瑪麗她們受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,我去引開那隻鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,以哥雷姆的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算被攻擊到了也能夠抵抗住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,趁這個時候  海特拉你去救出烏佐伊她們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我先觀察時機然後發射閃光彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,那隻鳥在慌亂後撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:48.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,要行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼  什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉  誘導的任務本應是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話更加靠譜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的命已經不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉他打算赴死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,與烏佐伊相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,我一直否定著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,每當她的笑顏和深情的愛對向我時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:47.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的內心深處都在呼喊著  我沒有那個資格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的救贖只能是拼上自己的性命去保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要擅自一個人結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,你要是選擇死亡逃避的話我絕對不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要一直待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,你就沒想如果我知道了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,我會殺掉你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是為你而存在的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果烏佐伊你願意的話  隨時都能夠獻上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,對  就在此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,那你就給我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:05.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要想用死來贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使多麼苦痛也要站起來走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:18.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後和我一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,這就是對你的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我向你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊果然真是個愛哭鬼
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比較著並排的影子相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕陽甩在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘風而去的是那小小的祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什麼是永遠  什麼是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我還一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道當我抬頭仰望你時  你的側臉總是那麼地閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牽著手傳遞的這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論何時都在給予我愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}這不斷溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到傳達到給你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向著共同許下的諾言和未來  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:41.06,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\blur5\pos(1561.067,1063.466)}向魔女尋求線索
